textBox.richText: Amy (aka Amalala on soundcloud) just came over to plan her debut DJ set selecting as Diggaboo. She’s doing the set to open the upcoming Bil Bless show with roomy and half of Splatinum Andrew Luck. You heard it here first, people: Jan 14 Bil Bless, Andrew Luck feat selector Diggaboo at the Loft in Sodo (Seattle) Listening to them plan the set now and daaaayum... . Their goal is to make people have sex on the dance floor. From the sound of it, we’re all fucked =) Check out Amy’s soundcloud here
